				<p>Herbs and spices are the key to vibrant and delectable dishes; we pick most of our herbs from our own garden in Hertfordshire and use fresh spices where possible. When using oil for cooking, coconut is our preference as it has a multitude of health benefits. However, our kitchen is also stocked with nut, seed and olive oils for use in our favourite dressings and sauces. 
